<h2 id="install-imfit">Install <a href="http://www.mpe.mpg.de/~erwin/code/imfit/markdown/index.html">Imfit</a></h2>

<p>Requirements: <a href="https://heasarc.gsfc.nasa.gov/docs/software/fitsio/fitsio_macosx.html">CFITSIO</a>, <a href="http://ftp.wayne.edu/gnu/gsl/">GNU Scientific Library</a>, <a href="http://www.fftw.org">FFTW</a> (which is used by many other packages as well), <a href="https://nlopt.readthedocs.io/en/latest/">NLopt</a>. You also need to install <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">CMake</code> by <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$ brew install cmake</code> to install <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">NLopt</code>. Almost all of these packages should be installed by <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$ ./configure &amp; make &amp; make install</code>. However, please check <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">INSTALL</code> file for more detailed description. You also need to install <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pip install scons</code>. After all these preparation, install <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">imfit</code> with <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$ scons ‚Äîno-openmp imfit &amp; scons ‚Äîno-openmp imfit-mcmc &amp; scons ‚Äîno-openmp makeimage</code>.</p>

